OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBishop says church should  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fallow gay marriage         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bishop of Oxford has said Church of
OL,6, England clergy should be able to bless 
OL,7, and marry gay couples.                 
OL,9,FThe Right Reverend Dr Steven Croft said
OL,10,Fhe was sorry his views on same-sex     
OL,11,Fmarriage were "slow to change" and had 
OL,12,F"caused genuine hurt, disagreement and 
OL,13,Fpain".                                 
OL,15,FIn an essay, he said clergy should also
OL,16,Fbe allowed to marry a same-sex partner 
OL,17,Fif they wished.                        
OL,19,FBy law no Church of England minister   
OL,20,Fcan bless or marry gay couples.        
